# Phase 0 Sources: Documentation & Methodology

## Overview
This directory contains the forensic reconstruction of the "Phase 0" genesis event of the Asymmetric Alliance. Unlike traditional narratives that place the start of this phenomenon in the mid-2010s, this data identifies the **2008 Financial Crisis** as the structural starting point.

The evidence is categorized into two vectors:
1.  **The Foreign Capture:** The acquisition of U.S. semiconductor assets by sovereign wealth funds.
2.  **The Domestic Reset:** The financial near-collapse and radical pivot of the U.S. "Oligarch Layer."

---

## Vector 1: The Foreign Capture (AMD & GlobalFoundries)

The primary evidence for the transfer of U.S. manufacturing sovereignty to the UAE (ATIC/Mubadala) relies on SEC filings, contemporary financial reporting, and Department of Defense records regarding the "Trusted Foundry" program.

### Primary Regulatory & Financial Documents
* **The "Asset Smart" Spin-off (SEC Filing):** The foundational document where AMD splits its design and manufacturing units.
    * [AMD 8-K Filing (Dec 8, 2008)](https://ir.amd.com/financial-information/sec-filings/content/0001193125-08-249520/dex991.htm)
    * [SEC Presentation on The Foundry Company](https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/2488/000119312508207049/dex991.htm)
* **CFIUS Approval:** Documentation of the Committee on Foreign Investment in the U.S. clearing the deal during the Bush-Obama transition.
    * [AMD Press Release on CFIUS Clearance](https://ir.amd.com/news-events/press-releases/detail/226/committee-on-foreign-investment-in-the-united-states-cfius-clears-path-for-creation-of-the-foundry-company)
    * [CFIUS Overview (Congressional Research Service)](https://www.congress.gov/crs_external_products/RL/PDF/RL33388/RL33388.77.pdf)
* **Trusted Foundry Status:** Proof of the paradox where a foreign-owned entity secures U.S. defense chips.
    * [GAO Report: Trusted Defense Microelectronics](https://www.gao.gov/assets/680/673876.pdf)
    * [Potomac Institute: Trusted State-of-the-Art Foundry Access](https://potomacinstitute.us/images/VITAL/TSFA-Exec-Summary.pdf)
    * [Special Security Agreement (Template/Example)](https://www.dcsa.mil/Portals/91/Documents/CTP/FOCI/SpecialSecurityAgreement-3-5-09.doc)

### Market Context & Sovereign Liquidity
* **Bailout Diplomacy:** Analysis of how Sovereign Wealth Funds recapitalized the West.
    * [Chicago Fed: The Role of Sovereign Wealth Funds](https://www.chicagofed.org/publications/chicago-fed-letter/2009/january-258)
    * [IMF: Sovereign Wealth Funds in the New Normal](https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/fandd/2010/06/erian.htm)
    * [Federal Reserve: Financial Crisis & Cross-Border Flows](https://www.federalreserve.gov/pubs/bulletin/2009/articles/crossborder/default.htm)
* **Mubadala/ATIC Reporting:**
    * [Mubadala Annual Report 2008](https://www.mubadala.com/en/news/mubadala-publishes-annual-report-for-2008)

