## Cultural Signals (The Zeitgeist of 2008)
To understand the *psychological* permissiveness of the era, we track cultural markers of institutional distrust.

* **Bitcoin Genesis Block (Jan 3, 2009):** [News on Genesis Block Message](https://blockworks.co/news/bitcoin-genesis-block-fifteeth-birthday). The embedded message "Chancellor on brink of second bailout" signals the rejection of central banking.
* **The Simpsons ("E Pluribus Wiggum"):** Aired Jan 6, 2008. Satirizes the hollowed-out political establishment susceptible to populism.
